x4freetext: Cross section measurements for the 16O+13C reaction at
the FN tandem accelerator of McMaster
a stainless steel target chamber, 7.5 cm in
diameter, lined inside with tantalum foil.
An HPGe detector of 40 cm3 sensitive volume
was placed at 125 degree with respect to the beam
direction, close to the target chamber.

supporting targets, were purchased from Atomic Energy
